estrictions, runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) | Venice Marco Polo (VCE/LIPZ) — CRIT: fog; visibility down to 100 m, cloud base around 100 ft; below alternate minima (current METAR) (drivers: low-visibility procedures (reduced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, approach minima limits) and 1 others. Changed since last run: Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO), Turku (TKU/EFTU), Stavanger Airport, Sola (SVG/ENZV), Lennart Meri Tallinn (TLL/EETN), Göteborg Landvetter (GOT/ESGG), Stockholm-Arlanda (ARN/ESSA), Mohammed V (CMN/GMMN), Trieste–Friuli Venezia Giulia (TRS/LIPQ), Maastricht Aachen (MST/EHBK), Plovdiv (PDV/LBPD) and 2 others.",
